  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/cab759cdd5bb8fb23338b6d189f18dcc.avif?t=1732115468\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras_big/cab759cdd5bb8fb23338b6d189f18dcc.avif?t=1732115468 width=800 height=440 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Echo Island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This island is currently experiencing a major real estate boom in several industry sectors. Together with your partner, Peter, you must build multiple constructions in this Boreal village. Gaining experience without causing too much damage will definitely help ensure your success. Work with new clients to extend your expertise and meet new challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/97f3e5f32b1a22505f9f69acebcd4970.poster.avif?t=1732115468\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/97f3e5f32b1a22505f9f69acebcd4970.webm?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/97f3e5f32b1a22505f9f69acebcd4970.mp4?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/a58f3b5449b3c3aeab20d5194dfa51b8.avif?t=1732115468\" width=800 height=427 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/fe24fa43eb82552edcaa27940ef028ba.poster.avif?t=1732115468\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/fe24fa43eb82552edcaa27940ef028ba.webm?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/fe24fa43eb82552edcaa27940ef028ba.mp4?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game highlights:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than  82 construction projects to carry out in the Echo Island village.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On this island, you will be expected to build a variety of constructions with various complexity levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A point system based on your construction: the more walls you destroy, the more points you lose at the end of the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock other characters to spice up your projects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control using a keyboard and mouse.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A user-friendly, seamless gameplay for the whole family.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Echo Island!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/0e65d6caeb6c933d85eabd36a9374b50.poster.avif?t=1732115468\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/0e65d6caeb6c933d85eabd36a9374b50.webm?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/0e65d6caeb6c933d85eabd36a9374b50.mp4?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/ed21a78b0c7c346638fc19ec091d2bd7.avif?t=1732115468\" width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/cab759cdd5bb8fb23338b6d189f18dcc.avif?t=1732115468\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras_big/cab759cdd5bb8fb23338b6d189f18dcc.avif?t=1732115468 width=800 height=440 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Echo Island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This island is currently experiencing a major real estate boom in several industry sectors. Together with your partner, Peter, you must build multiple constructions in this Boreal village. Gaining experience without causing too much damage will definitely help ensure your success. Work with new clients to extend your expertise and meet new challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/97f3e5f32b1a22505f9f69acebcd4970.poster.avif?t=1732115468\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/97f3e5f32b1a22505f9f69acebcd4970.webm?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/97f3e5f32b1a22505f9f69acebcd4970.mp4?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/a58f3b5449b3c3aeab20d5194dfa51b8.avif?t=1732115468\" width=800 height=427 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/fe24fa43eb82552edcaa27940ef028ba.poster.avif?t=1732115468\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/fe24fa43eb82552edcaa27940ef028ba.webm?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/fe24fa43eb82552edcaa27940ef028ba.mp4?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game highlights:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than  82 construction projects to carry out in the Echo Island village.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On this island, you will be expected to build a variety of constructions with various complexity levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A point system based on your construction: the more walls you destroy, the more points you lose at the end of the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock other characters to spice up your projects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control using a keyboard and mouse.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A user-friendly, seamless gameplay for the whole family.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Echo Island!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/0e65d6caeb6c933d85eabd36a9374b50.poster.avif?t=1732115468\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/0e65d6caeb6c933d85eabd36a9374b50.webm?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/0e65d6caeb6c933d85eabd36a9374b50.mp4?t=1732115468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113740/extras/ed21a78b0c7c346638fc19ec091d2bd7.avif?t=1732115468\" width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
